masuk mengembangkan ide pembuatan Karya Tulis Ilmiah.\r\nPaguyuban KSE USU memiliki logo seperti tiga orang dengan warna yang berbeda yang saling bergandengan tangan. Makna tiga orang tersebut adalah menggambarkan Sprit KSE yaitu Sharing, Networking dan Developing. Saling bergandengan dalam logo artinya menjalin kekeluargaan antar penerima beasiswa KSE. Warna yang berbeda di logo mencerminkan keberagaman yang ada pada penerima beasiswa KSE, namun menjadi satu keluarga, yaitu Keluarga Paguyuban KSE USU. Semoga semangat KSE selalu membara pada setiap penerima. KSE Jaya Jaya Jaya.','Profil','','inherit','closed','closed','','20-revision-v1','','','2019-02-19 05:07:43','2019-02-18 22:07:43','',20,'http://localhost/paguyubankseusu/2019/02/19/20-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(83,1,'2019-02-19 05:17:12','2019-02-18 22:17:12','','HUT Paguyuban KSE USU','','publish','open','closed','','hut-paguyuban-kse-usu','','','2019-07-09 04:03:33','2019-07-08 21:03:33','',0,'http://localhost/paguyubankseusu/?post_type=dt_gallery&#038;p=83',0,'dt_gallery','',0),(84,1,'2019-02-19 05:17:12','2019-02-18 22:17:12','','HUT Paguyuban KSE USU','','inherit','closed','closed','','83-revision-v1','','','2019-02-19 05:17:12','2019-02-18 22:17:12','',83,'http://localhost/paguyubankseusu/2019/02/19/83-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(86,1,'2019-02-19 05:27:44','2019-02-18 22:27:44','','2a2db8785149ff38f84a0d82f9c2abb1','','inherit','open','closed','','2a2db8785149ff38f84a0d82f9c2abb1','','','2019-02-19 05:27:44','2019-02-18 22:27:44','',0,'http://localhost/paguyubankseusu/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/2a2db8785149ff38f84a0d82f9c2abb1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(87,1,'2019-02-19 05:27:49','2019-02-18 22:27:49','','3a7a44421acfaaeb43fd969e4dbba514','','inherit','open','closed','','3a7a44421acfaaeb43fd969e4dbba514','','','2019-02-19 05:27:49','2019-02-18 22:27:49','',0,'http://localhost/paguyubankseusu/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/3a7a44421acfaaeb43fd969e4dbba514.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg'