Bapak/Ibu donator KSE yang selama ini memberikan bantuan dana buat <em>gue</em>. Alhamdulillah semoga Allah SWT membalas kebaikan bapak/Ibu donator sekalian.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','Dibalik Uang 600K pada Setiap Awal Bulan','','inherit','closed','closed','','478-revision-v1','','','2019-05-04 12:59:07','2019-05-04 05:59:07','',478,'http://www.paguyubankseusu.org/2019/05/04/478-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(480,1,'2019-05-06 07:00:09','2019-05-06 00:00:09','KSE FUN DAY merupakan salah satu program kerja dari Divisi Human Resource Development KSE USU, berupa refreshing serta hiburan untuk mempererat rasa kekeluargaan di Paguyuban KSE USU. Pada priode ini, KSE FUN DAY diadakan di Paropo (01/05). Wahh, ini namanya libur mantap jiwa versi KSE.\r\nKamu liburan kemana hari ini?\r\n\r\nWith love,\r\nPaguyuban KSE USU💕\r\n\r\nSHARING-NETWORKING-DEVELOPING\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-482\" src=\"http://www.paguyubankseusu.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/KSE-FUNDAY_190505_0125-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-483\" src=\"http://www.paguyubankseusu.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/KSE-FUNDAY_190505_0133-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-481\" src=\"http://www.paguyubankseusu.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/KSE-FUNDAY_190505_0010-e1557040467388-300x236.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"236\" />','KSE Fun Day','','publish','open','open','','kse-fun-day-2','','','2019-05-05 14:28:38','2019-05-05 07:28:38','',0,'http://www.paguyubankseusu.org/?p=480',0,'post','',0),(481,1,'2019-05-05 14:13:49','2019-05-05 07:13:49','','KSE FUNDAY_190505_0010','','inherit','open','closed','','kse-funday_190505_0010','','','2019-05-05 14:13:49','2019-05-05 07:13:49','',480,'http://www.paguyubankseusu.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/KSE-FUNDAY_190505_0010.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(482,1,'2019-05-05 14:13:53','2019-05-05 07:13:53','','KSE FUNDAY_1